	measure 'Target Dso' = ```
			
			VAR target =
			    CALCULATE (
			        SUM ( 'FACT_GSheet_Target_Shop_Daily'[Target] ),
			        'FACT_GSheet_Target_Shop_Daily'[Type] = "DSO TARGET"
			    )
			VAR dso_iP17 =
			    CALCULATE (
			        [Dso],
			        FILTER (
			            'FACT_Sale_Doanh số bán',
			            CONTAINSSTRING ( 'FACT_Sale_Doanh số bán'[ProductCode], "APP-IP17" )
			            || CONTAINSSTRING ( 'FACT_Sale_Doanh số bán'[ProductCode], "APP-IP-AIR" )
			        ),
			        FILTER (
			            'FACT_Sale_Doanh số bán',
			            'FACT_Sale_Doanh số bán'[Date] >= DATE ( 2025, 9, 19 )
			            && 'FACT_Sale_Doanh số bán'[Date] <= DATE ( 2025, 9, 24 )
			        )
			    )
			RETURN
			    target + dso_iP17
			
			```
		displayFolder: 2. Chỉ tiêu
		lineageTag: 1de6b6cc-30c6-45ed-9907-7be8f62aa43d

